<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Sports — Games Landing</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<style>
  :root {
    --field: #1c8a3e;
    --field-dark: #0f5a26;
    --line: #ffffff;
    --jersey-red: #c8102e;
    --jersey-navy: #0c2340;
    --gold: #f8c61c;
    --whistle: #fefcf6;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: "Helvetica Neue", "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
    background:
      repeating-linear-gradient(
        90deg,
        var(--field) 0 80px,
        var(--field-dark) 80px 160px
      );
    color: #fff;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 40px 24px 80px;
  }
  header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    max-width: 1240px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  .banner {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--jersey-red) 0%, #8a0a20 100%);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 8px 24px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 13px;
    border-top: 4px solid var(--gold);
    border-bottom: 4px solid var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 22px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(40px, 7vw, 96px);
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #fff;
    text-shadow:
      3px 3px 0 var(--jersey-navy),
      6px 6px 0 var(--gold),
      8px 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
  }
  .sub {
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 18px;
    opacity: 0.92;
  }
  nav { margin-top: 22px; }
  nav a {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--jersey-navy);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 12px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 2px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(330px, 1fr));
    gap: 28px;
    max-width: 1240px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .card {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--whistle);
    color: var(--jersey-navy);
    border-radius: 14px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
    border: 3px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .stripe {
    height: 14px;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
      45deg,
      var(--jersey-red) 0 14px,
      var(--whistle) 14px 28px,
      var(--jersey-navy) 28px 42px,
      var(--whistle) 42px 56px
    );
  }
  .shot-wrap {
    position: relative;
    padding: 14px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 0%, #efece2 100%);
  }
  .shot {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16/10;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--field);
    border: 2px solid var(--jersey-navy);
  }
  .ribbon {
    position: absolute;
    top: 22px; left: -8px;
    background: var(--jersey-red);
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 6px 14px 6px 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 92% 50%, 100% 100%, 0 100%);
  }
  .body { padding: 18px 20px 22px; }
  h2 {
    margin: 0 0 6px;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 900;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .meta {
    color: var(--jersey-red);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 11px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .prompt {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    min-height: 92px;
  }
  .play {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--jersey-navy);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 12px 22px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 13px;
    border-bottom: 4px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .play:hover { background: var(--jersey-red); border-bottom-color: var(--jersey-navy); }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="banner">★ Season Highlights ★ Six Sports ★</div>
    <h1>The Sports Pack</h1>
    <div class="sub">Hit play. Pick a team. Beat the clock.</div>
    <nav><a href="index.html">← All themes</a></nav>
  </header>

  <main class="grid">
    <article class="card">
      <div class="stripe"></div>
      <div class="shot-wrap">
        <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/mini-soccer"><img class="shot" src="https://mini-soccer--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a>
      </div>
      <span class="ribbon">Soccer</span>
      <div class="body">
        <h2>Mini Soccer</h2>
        <div class="meta">1 v 1 · Top-Down · First to 3</div>
        <p class="prompt">Arrow keys move, space kicks. AI opponent on a small pitch. First to three goals wins, stadium crowd-cue when you score.</p>
        <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/mini-soccer">▶ Play</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <div class="stripe"></div>
      <div class="shot-wrap">
        <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/swish-shooter"><img class="shot" src="https://swish-shooter--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a>
      </div>
      <span class="ribbon">Basketball</span>
      <div class="body">
        <h2>Hoop Shot</h2>
        <div class="meta">Free Throws · 10 Shots</div>
        <p class="prompt">Drag-and-release to aim direction and power; arc shifts with power. Ten shots per round, perfect-swish bonuses, wooden-gym backdrop.</p>
        <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/swish-shooter">▶ Play</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <div class="stripe"></div>
      <div class="shot-wrap">
        <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/net-game"><img class="shot" src="https://net-game--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a>
      </div>
      <span class="ribbon">Tennis</span>
      <div class="body">
        <h2>Tennis Rally</h2>
        <div class="meta">Best of 5 · Click to Swing</div>
        <p class="prompt">Side-view tennis vs AI. Click to swing as the ball arrives. Best-of-five rallies on a grass court with crisp white lines.</p>
        <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/net-game">▶ Play</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <div class="stripe"></div>
      <div class="shot-wrap">
        <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/mini-golf"><img class="shot" src="https://mini-golf--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a>
      </div>
      <span class="ribbon">Mini Golf</span>
      <div class="body">
        <h2>Golf Putt</h2>
        <div class="meta">9 Holes · Putting</div>
        <p class="prompt">Aim with mouse, set power with a charging bar, putt across nine holes with windmills and ramps. Top-down view, scorecard kept.</p>
        <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/mini-golf">▶ Play</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <div class="stripe"></div>
      <div class="shot-wrap">
        <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/hundred-meter-dash"><img class="shot" src="https://hundred-meter-dash--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a>
      </div>
      <span class="ribbon">Track</span>
      <div class="body">
        <h2>Track Dash</h2>
        <div class="meta">100m · Arrow Mash</div>
        <p class="prompt">Alternate left/right arrow keys as fast as possible to accelerate. Race three AI runners in a stadium-track view with lane markings.</p>
        <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/hundred-meter-dash">▶ Play</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <div class="stripe"></div>
      <div class="shot-wrap">
        <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/lane-strike"><img class="shot" src="https://lane-strike--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a>
      </div>
      <span class="ribbon">Bowling</span>
      <div class="body">
        <h2>Bowling Strike</h2>
        <div class="meta">10 Frames · Drag & Roll</div>
        <p class="prompt">Drag to aim, drag again to set power, watch the ball roll. Ten frames per game with proper strike-and-spare scoring.</p>
        <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/lane-strike">▶ Play</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
